create.description: Creates an auth config record. Fetch corresponding credentials for specific auth types, e.g. access token for OAuth 2.0, JWT token for JWT. Encrypt the auth config with Cloud KMS and store the encrypted credentials in Spanner. Returns the encrypted auth config.

patch.description: Updates an auth config. If credential is updated, fetch the encrypted auth config from Spanner, decrypt with Cloud KMS key, update the credential fields, re-encrypt with Cloud KMS key and update the Spanner record. For other fields, directly update the Spanner record. Returns the encrypted auth config.
